		font-size: 1.4rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.section-title:not(:last-child) {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	@media screen and (min-width: 1280px) {
		.short-tag {
			font-size: 2rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

